    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible, mint condition that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this beauty since day one\u2014it's been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
