      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive rod bearing service, addressing the critical mechanical requirements of the chassis. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides precise, short-throw shifts, delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings, ensuring the telepathic handling characteristics these cars are known for. This is a mechanically pristine, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
