      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark or rock chip, while the interior is a pristine sanctuary, still carrying that distinct factory-new scent. Every piece of leather is supple and uncreased, and the dashboard is flawless. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service documented. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of road wear. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
